            </li>
            <li xml:id="auto_ml335ych">
                <p xml:id="auto_qhyplz70">
                    Draw a trapezium and label its bases, legs, and height.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li xml:id="auto_5v01903a">
                <p xml:id="auto_of8vd930">
                    How many angles does a trapezium have? What is the sum of all interior angles?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li xml:id="auto_4c77udg2">
                <p xml:id="auto_rh0jpfm7">
